title: Ep. 7 - Who do I think I am?
itunes:title: Ep. 7 - Who do I think I am?
description: It can happen to anyone, and it quite frequently does. Wendy wrestles with imposter syndrome and pins it to the mat. She shares some tools to quiet that voice in your head that, if left to its own devices, can rob us of all the incredible things we were meant to do and be.
